    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078750/extras/6c56a422ccdda20a1067fb618ac71606.avif?t=1728068166\" width=620 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raid &amp; Fortress is a continuation for The Scorchfarer. Exactly where the first episode left off, we now follow the deuteragonists Ika and Agnes, who find themselves trapped inside of their own academy after an arrest has gone awry. While they try to figure out the truth, the South Commanders have been assembled to raid the place in order to free them from their mysterious captors.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078750/extras/b5968a9e92dd7849de214480e3250240.avif?t=1728068166\" width=620 height=271 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 NEW hand drawn characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 6 NEW versions of already existing characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 61 NEW hand drawn backgrounds (+14 variations) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 67 NEW hand drawn animations and spreads </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 13 NEW original songs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 to 6 hours in length (second episode) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >23 NEW sparks for you to discover </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More Journal and Observatorium entries </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More achievements </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Episode 2 length is double of the first episode and features thrice as much art.</p>",
